2002_August 10 

 When i played the game i have always wanted a movie about this game. Then
when it came on video i was not so impressed with the film because the movie
did not have alot to do with the game it only had the basic thing....the
T-virus and zombies. But overall it is a good film for people who like
horror/action films.<br /><br />  6/10 stars.
